description: The Notebook Project is a social benefit corporation built around a fully interactive platform featuring a growing database of career-related topics, financial literacy programs, free webinars, curated audiobooks, and top-rated online courses. This platform is essentially powered by a network of instructors, mentors, authors, content creators and publishers. Local businesses and volunteers are invited to participate or sponsor a reading group to make this initiative as impactful as possible...
name: The Notebook Project
